Federal Register: 154. Methazole (2-(3,4-dichlorophenyl)-4-methyl-1,2,4-oxadiazolidine-3,5-dione) (CAS No. 020354-26-1) (FIFRA AI) (Ref. 3). Rabbits receiving 30 or 60 mg/kg/day by gavage on days 6 to 18 of gestation exhibited increased embryolethality. The NOEL was 10 mg/kg/day. EPA believes that there is sufficient evidence for listing methazole on EPCRA section 313 pursuant to EPCRA section 313(d)(2)(B) based on the available developmental toxicity data for this chemical.
